If your basic theory of ESG investing is =E2=80=9Cwe will avoid bad-ESG sto=
cks in order to drive up the cost of capital of bad-ESG things,=E2=80=9D it=
 seems to be working:Years of awful returns and pressure from clients to ex=
it from the oil-and-gas business have left fewer and smaller firms able to =
take advantage of rising prices and help boost production. The unwillingnes=
