Legendary bond and fixed income investor William H. (Bill) Gross today rele=
ased a new Investment Outlook, =E2=80=98You Only Hang Twice.=E2=80=99=E2=80=
=9D) Is it the weirdest monthly investor letter ever written? Quite possibl=
y? If it qualifies as an investor letter at all?=C2=A0It leads off with Gro=
ss=E2=80=99s version of how he was found in contempt of court for playing m=
usic too loud at night by =E2=80=9Cthe hanging judge of the Laguna Beach sh=
ore, a 57-year-old lady with pierced nose stud and visible tattoos,=E2=80=
=9D and=C2=A0given a five-day suspended jail sentence, community service an=
d =E2=80=9Ca mere $1,200 fine.=E2=80=9D (This is all framed by the conceit =
that a new James Bond movie=C2=A0is being made about the affair, starring J=
